(190, 1, '2019-08-27 06:48:24', '2019-08-27 06:48:24', '<div class=\"about-us-top\">\r\n<figure><img src=\"[contenturl type=templateurl]/images/thumbnails/thumb-39100935.jpg\" class=\"thumb_right_dd\" alt=\"smiling male worker in yellow forklift\"></figure>\r\nGlobal Logistics Group - GLG is one of the fastest growing third-party logistics providers in the transportation industry. We offer the latest equipment, workforce, and expertise for high-quality freight brokerage and trucking logistics in Stafford, Virginia.\r\n\r\nOur team of experts can identify the right transport solutions for any destination to the size, weight, or mode. If you’re transporting domestic shipments within North America, our local market experts draw on our range of resources for ground and air expedited transportation.\r\n\r\n<div id=\"mission\" class=\"nh_m\">\r\n<h5>Our Mission <span>Statement</span></h5>\r\n<p>Our mission is to deliver quality transportation services at fair and affordable rates. Unlike many transportation companies today, we maintain pride in what we do. Our company policies are built on common courtesy and the Golden Rule, not just the bare minimum set by state and national logistics standards. We will always treat your freight as if it was ours.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"clearme\"><strong>Why Choose GLG?</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"faq\">\r\n  <h6 id=\"nh_1\">Shipping Anywhere in America</h6>\r\n  <div>We mobilize a dynamic network of shippers and carriers prepared to deliver any kind of shipment intact and on time.</div>\r\n  <h6 id=\"nh_2\">The Best Service Always Guaranteed</h6>\r\n  <div>Our experts provide custom solutions that meet every client’s unique transport requirements. Customer satisfaction is always our priority.</div>\r\n  <h6 id=\"nh_3\">Effective Logistics Solutions</h6>\r\n  <div>We always maintain the highest standards of quality from the pick-up to the drop-off. We don’t waste your time or your money.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\nIf you